Trafalgar House Plc &lt;TRAF.L> said it hasacquired the entire share capital of &lt;Capital Homes Inc> of theU.S. For 20 mln dlrs in cash.    Capital Homes builds single family homes in the WashingtonD.C. Area and is also active as a land developer both for itsown use and for sale to other builders.    In the financial year to end February, 1987, Capitalrecorded pre-tax profits of 3.7 mln dlrs on a turnover of 58mln dlrs from the sale of 421 homes. Capital has a land bank ofsome 2,600 units and in the current year the company expects tosell 500 homes, Trafalgar House said. REUTER&#3;